{
  "title": "Join Us",
  "description": "Marine Life 2030 is implemented utilizing a bottom-up approach which relies on volunteers from all around the world. A series of learning communities have been established, focused on:  \r\n\r\nBest Practices and Interoperability \r\n\r\nCo-design and Stakeholder Engagement \r\n\r\nCapacity Development Citizen Science \r\n\r\nEarly Career Ocean Professionals (ECOPS) \r\n\r\nExternal Communications and",
